title: My YouTube Channel - Come check it out / links in description x

embed.description: Hey guys and welcome to my first gaming video! League of Lee Sin #1 In this episode I'm basically just running around playing a normal game and added in the funny parts and edits to make it a little more enjoyable :P Hope that you guys enjoy it and please give any constructive critisism as I'm looking to expand and keep this going, maybe even start streaming one day.

body:
**League of Legends - League of Lee Sin #1**


Hello and welcome to my small post just cheekily promoting my new YouTube channel. I'm going to be trying to upload videos once a week at least possibly more if people enjoy them. Please jump on over and support me by hitting the like button commenting and even subscribing if you want to see more. 

PS. I would love to get some constructive criticism because it will allow me to make better YouTube videos. 

Anyway if you want to add me in-game feel free to.

IGN: *diranpanda*
